tion</code>.</p>\n<p><code>null</code> zwracane jest także, gdy węzeł został utworzony, ale nie przypisano go jeszcze do drzewa.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_tak.c5.bce","title":"Zobacz także","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/firstChild\"><code>element.firstChild</code></a>, <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/lastChild\"><code>element.lastChild</code></a>, <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/childNodes\"><code>element.childNodes</code></a>, <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/nextSibling\"><code>element.nextSibling</code></a>, <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/previousSibling\"><code>element.previousSibling</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-1060184317\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 Core: Node.parentNode</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect1\">\n &nbsp;</div>\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Własność parentNode zwraca rodzica bieżącego elementu.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.parentNode","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Node.parentNode","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Node.parentNode","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.parentNode","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.parentNode","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Node.parentNode","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Node.parentNode","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.parentNode","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/node/parentnode","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/node/parentnode/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Tec